Deb Shops Inc said its boarddeclared a 100 pct stock dividend and will increase thequarterly dividend to four cts from 3-1/4 cts after adjustm,entfor the split.    The company said the split is payable April 17 to holdersof record March 25.  The dividend increase will be effectivewith the April 30 payment, it said. Reuter&#3;